name: Woman's body 2
description:
Woman's body 2 is the second part of the game series "Woman's body". This is a card game with images of different female body parts that will test your memory. The aim of the game is to find pairs of cards. This part of the game is aimed at an adult audience. In this game you will look at the female parts of the body, remember their appearance, and then find a pair of cards.

Game Features:
- Different levels of difficulty. From simple to complex.
- 43 cards with images of beautiful girls.
- It develops memory and is suitable only for adults.
- 18 levels. Ranging from easy and ending with large and complex levels.
